snippet.title: NDA - Billie Eilish (live acoustic cover) | her habits
snippet.description:
My attempt at covering Billie Eilish's new song "NDA" from her upcoming album "Happier Than Ever" live via ancient out of tune piano in my dingy basement. 

#BillieEilish #NDA #HappierThanEver
